data.description: This house has so much to offer! The newly PAINTED EXTERIOR in 2022 and mature landscape create inviting CURB APPEAL. From the moment you enter you are welcomed into the main level with an UPGRADED kitchen and open floor plan that leads out to the WIDE OPEN backyard just ready for you to create your own Desert Oasis. Upstairs, you enter into a large, flexible LOFT space and nook area perfect for a desk. In one direction you head into the owners retreat where you will fall in love with the WALK IN closet and UPDATED en suite, in the opposite direction are two additional bedrooms, creating a desirable SPLIT BEDROOM layout. What an INCREDIBLE opportunity. NEW AC 2018!
